name: Friendship
description: A portrait of my younger brother and the cat he has cared for since childhood called Denko. He named it Denko from the powdered milk brand because its white fur. Sometimes I think about my brother condition if someday his beloved cat will go first. Because from what we know the age of a cat is faster than the age of humans. My brother really loves this white cat with all his heart, because according to him, by taking care of the cat, my brother gets the happiness that he can't get from anything else.
